pageContext.description: Width mouth: 41.5mm; width edge 52mm; width loop 12.3mm; breadth mouth 40.5mm; depth socket 69.5mm,Single protuberant moulding; two grooves set just inside the corners of either face; area between flattish, but hammer dented; small punchmarks on lower blade aligned along axis; base of casting flash hammer-flattened; some lipping around mouth with one protruberant  runner stump; edge-bevel v. close to edge; flat narrow rectangular socket end.
pageContext.patina: Dark green patina; small areas of granular lighter green surface.
pageContext.surface: Edge mainly intact, fairly sharp; some scratching at edge possibly recent; light orange-brown soil adhering.
